<i>Freedom</i> on the left.
<i>independence</i> on the right.

1281
01:14:12.699 --> 01:14:16.411
All right. We're going left here.

1282
01:14:16.494 --> 01:14:19.956
To the right is fuel gauge.
You watch the fuel gauge.

1283
01:14:20.040 --> 01:14:26.504
150. okay. 160. okay.
200. bad disaster for space station.

1284
01:14:26.588 --> 01:14:29.674
So if you watch 200.
you can call for Lev. on.

1285
01:14:29.758 --> 01:14:32.802
and you see here number one. on.
You ask for Lev.

1286
01:14:32.886 --> 01:14:34.804
